<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1430] SSTable statistics causing intermittent CL test failures in trunk.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1430</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Testcase: testCleanup(org.apache.cassandra.db.CommitLogTest):	FAILED&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; 2 != 1&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; junit.framework.AssertionFailedError: 2 != 1&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; 	at org.apache.cassandra.db.CommitLogTest.testCleanup(CommitLogTest.java:69)&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I see this 1-2 times a day.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
